e_name": "videocover.png", "id": "1856125128361075", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035403_1856125131694408_3239532312285045631_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Vo3aNgkxlJIQ7kNvgG5ZOug&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AHB_VsmIxxn4CkfOTbxUbK1&oh=00_AYBDtj2wg37L-SmVZJHzSl0PpQsAu0AHPYZja4phb_vwrw&oe=66ED4DB3"}, "display_name": "AI Therapist: Your Emotional Guide", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Welcome to AI Therapist: Your Emotional Guide, an innovative journey into emotional well-being powered by artificial intelligence. This app bridges technology and human emotions, enabling users to have natural and meaningful conversations with a generative AI therapist that responds with understanding and relevance.\n\nAI Therapist provides a non-judgmental space for individuals to explore their feelings, thoughts, and emotions. Whether seeking reflection, support, or new ways to connect with your inner self, AI Therapist delivers realistic interactions for a deeper understanding of emotions.\n\nKey Features:\n\n\u2022 Immersive 3D interface for engaging therapy sessions.\n\u2022 Realistic AI conversations for emotional support.\n\u2022 A safe platform for self-discovery and growth.\n\u2022 Perfect for daily check-ins, with an AI that offers effective assistance.\n\nNote: AI Therapist is experimental and not a substitute for professional therapy. It represents a step towards leveraging AI for emotional well-being, offering companionship on the path to self-improvement.", "short_description": "Explore emotions with AI: AI Therapist: Your Emotional Guide offers innovative therapy sessions with generative AI for emotional self-discovery. Experience natural conversations where the AI understands and guides you through your feelings, creating a unique space for emotional exploration."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://doc-hosting.flycricket.io/ai-therapist-your-emotional-guide-privacy-policy/2d3288f